Package: evfuse
Title: Spatial Data Fusion for Extreme Value Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brian", "White", email = "bwhite@wakehealth.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Two-stage frequentist framework for fusing multiple spatial data
    sources with extreme value margins. Fits pointwise GEV distributions at
    observed sites, then estimates a multivariate Gaussian process with
    coregionalization structure via maximum likelihood. Supports kriging with
    partial observations, return level estimation, and uncertainty quantification
    via delta method and simulation.
